<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "4A">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "ASPAP70A4106021" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Comprobación de la función del servofreno 
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Antes de realizar esta comprobación, asegúrese de que no hay aire en la tubería hidráulica. 
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servinfosub id = "ASPAP70A4106021001">
<title>
Comprobación de la estanqueidad al aire 
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ponga el motor en marcha. 
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Detenga el motor tras 1 a 2 minutos en funcionamiento. 
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pise varias veces el pedal de freno con la misma fuerza que en el caso del frenado ordinario para observar cómo cambia el recorrido del pedal. El servofreno es hermético si el juego del pedal se reduce cada vez que se pisa el pedal. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.619mm" ver = "01" gw = "131" gh = "126"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.501in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.579in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.631in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1ª
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
2ª
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
3ª
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Si el juego del pedal no cambia, el servofreno presenta una avería en su hermetismo. 
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Si se detectan defectos, inspeccione los tubos de vacío y las partes selladas, y sustituya las piezas defectuosas. Tras ello, repita toda la prueba. 
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.196mm" ver = "01" gw = "132" gh = "125"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.030in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1ª, 2ª, 3ª
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "ASPAP70A4106021002">
<title>
Comprobación del funcionamiento 
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Con el motor parado, pise el pedal del freno varias veces con la misma fuerza y asegúrese de que el recorrido del pedal no cambie. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.323mm" ver = "01" gw = "162" gh = "126"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Arranque el motor con el pedal de freno pisado. Si el recorrido del pedal aumenta ligeramente, el funcionamiento del servofreno será correcto. Si no existe ningún cambio en el juego del pedal, esto indica una avería del servofreno. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410008.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.958mm" ver = "01" gw = "173" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "ASPAP70A4106021003">
<title>
Inspección de la estanqueidad al aire en estado de carga 
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Con el motor funcionando, pise el pedal de freno. Después pare el motor manteniendo el pedal de freno pisado. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410009.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.805mm" ver = "01" gw = "123" gh = "130"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.232in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.628in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Mantener 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Mantenga el pedal pisado durante 30 segundos. Si la altura del pedal no cambia, el servofreno se encuentra en buen estado. Si la altura del pedal cambia, el servofreno no se encuentra en buen estado. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.059mm" ver = "01" gw = "192" gh = "131"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.643in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.800in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Mantener 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
T: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
30 segundos
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
